column1: Growth-irradiance curve parameters and other information for all experiments used in the paper. The columns include: species (species name), mu_max (µmax, d-1), alpha (α, d-1 µmol photons-1 m2 s1), I_opt (Iopt, µmol photons m-2 s-1), I_max (the maximum irradiance used in the experiment, µmol photons m-2 s-1), culture temperature (°C), culture daylength (h), cell volume (µm3), taxon, environment (C = coastal, O = oceanic), Chl:C (mass ratio, measured under the lowest irradiance), and reference. In some cases the model-estimated Iopt can be very high, suggesting no evidence for photoinhibition in the experiment. We have included the maximum irradiance used in the experiment for comparison.
